Title: DateTime.toParts
Category: function
Module Path: effect/DateTime
Export Kind: const
Category Tag: parts

Description: Get the different parts of a `DateTime` as an object. The parts will be time zone adjusted if the `DateTime` is zoned.

Signature: toParts: (self: DateTime) => DateTime.PartsWithWeekday = Internal.toParts

Example:
```ts
import { DateTime } from "effect"

const dt = DateTime.makeUnsafe("2024-01-01T12:30:45.123Z")
const parts = DateTime.toParts(dt)

console.log(parts)
// {
//   year: 2024,
//   month: 1,
//   day: 1,
//   hours: 12,
//   minutes: 30,
//   seconds: 45,
//   millis: 123,
//   weekDay: 1 // Monday
// }
```

