Description: This module provides utilities for working with mutable references in a functional context. A Ref is a mutable reference that can be read, written, and atomically modified. Unlike plain mutable variables, Refs are thread-safe and work seamlessly with Effect's concurrency model. They provide atomic operations for safe state management in concurrent programs.

